articles.description: Duke freshman Marvin Bagley III will miss his third straight game Sunday against No. 11 Clemson as he continues to recover from a 'mild' right knee sprain suffered in the first half against North Carolina last week.
articles.headline: Marvin Bagley III to miss third straight game Sunday with right knee sprain

articles.description: Michigan State holds Northwestern to 11 points in the second half and Cassius Winston finishes with 17 points and 9 rebounds as the Spartans win 65-60.
